{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"uw1ie7bctc50l5lz3cytw4i","title":"Constructor Connected Callback","desc":"","updated":1687570593470,"created":1687488786121,"nav_order":1,"custom":{"nav_order":1},"fname":"web-components.lifecycle.constructor-connected-callback","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"4ad53c1bdab6e1cb84e5bcc1bc442981","links":[],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"gxmnngmtnylxfipxr0980ej","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"constructor-connected-callback\">Constructor Connected Callback<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#constructor-connected-callback\"></a></h1>\n<pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">XComponent</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">HTMLElement</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">constructor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> \n    <span class=\"token keyword\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> \n\n  <span class=\"token function\">connectedCallback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> \n    <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">innerHTML</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Hello World from a Web Component!'</span> \n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\ncustomElements<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">define</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'x-component'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">XComponent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>El constructor se ejecuta cada vez que una instancia del componente se crea. Sin embargo, si tenemos que instanciar al DOM o ejecutar la lógica inicial, vamos a querer correr este código en el <code>connectedCallback()</code> hook. Este se ejecuta cuando un componente se agrega al DOM, después de eso podemos empezar a renderizar e interactuar con el DOM.</p>","noteIndex":{"id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1687570355610,"created":1687478467553,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"503e0f736c7c1d0c26ed87839ccd08a9","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"https://webcomponent.dev/","alias":"Cory Rylan","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":94,"offset":117},"end":{"line":4,"column":134,"offset":157},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"https://webcomponent.dev/"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"web-components.Apis.custom-elements","alias":"Custom Elements","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":3,"offset":227},"end":{"line":9,"column":60,"offset":284},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"web-components.Apis.custom-elements"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"web-components.Apis.shadow-dom","alias":"Shadow Dow","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":3,"offset":287},"end":{"line":10,"column":49,"offset":333},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"web-components.Apis.shadow-dom"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id"